Zip and upload to Canvas: all .java source files + replicase_rscu.csv + spike_rscu.csv + rscu_comparison.csv + spike_favored.txt.

Key Formulas
RSCU = O / E
E = (total count of all codons for that amino acid) / (number of synonymous codons for that amino acid)
UP = category becomes more favored going from replicase → spike
DOWN = category becomes less favored going from replicase → spike
Blank = no category change

